Tzatziki

Ingredient
1. Grated cucumber 
2. 1 1/2 cup of Greek Yoghurt
3. 2 tbsp extra virgin olive oil
4. 2 tbsp chopped fresh mint/dill
5. 1 tbsp lemon juice
6. 1 garlic clove grated
7. 1/2 teaspoon fine sea salt

Method
1. Add grated cucumber into bowl and add rest of the ingredients
2. Allow mixture to rest for 5 min then chilled for later
